'''Papa John's Pizza'''（在中國大陸譯作「'''棒！约翰'''」）是一家美國的餐廳公司。該公司營運世界第三大[[外賣店|外賣]]和比薩餅外送[[連鎖店|連鎖]][[餐馆|餐館]]，其總部在[[路易斯維爾_(肯塔基州)|路易斯維爾]]郊區的{{link-en|傑佛遜鎮 (肯塔基州)|Jeffersontown, Kentucky|傑佛遜鎮}}。<ref>"[http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/1719477221.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+07%2C+2007&author=&pub=Courier+-+Journal&desc=Jeffersontown+to+dedicate+new+bike+and+walking+path+Saturday&pqatl=google Jeffersontown to dedicate new bike and walking path Saturday]." ''[[The_Courier-Journal|The Courier-Journal]]''. November 7, 2007. C7. Retrieved on December 6, 2012. "Papa John's office is in Jeffersontown,"</ref><ref>"[http://www.papajohns.com/pizzachallenge/index.shtm Papa's Specialty Pizza Challenge] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023034743/http://www.papajohns.com/pizzachallenge/index.shtm |date=2014-10-23 }}." Papa John's Pizza. Retrieved on December 6, 2012. "Papa John's International Inc., 2002 Papa John's Blvd, Louisville, KY 40299."</ref><ref>"[http://www2.census.gov/geo/maps/dc10map/GUBlock/st21_ky/place/p2140222_jeffersontown/DC10BLK_P2140222_001.pdf 2010 CENSUS – CENSUS BLOCK MAP (INDEX): Jeffersontown city, KY 1] {{Wayback|url=http://www2.census.gov/geo/maps/dc10map/GUBlock/st21_ky/place/p2140222_jeffersontown/DC10BLK_P2140222_001.pdf |date=20140326093739 }}." [[U.S._Census_Bureau|U.S. Census Bureau]]. Retrieved on December 7, 2012.</ref><ref name="chain2">{{cite web |url=http://www.freep.com/article/20130625/BUSINESS/306250105/Top-7-pizza-chains-Little-Caesars-moves-up-a-notch |title=Little Caesars rises to nation's No. 3 pizza chain with $2.9B in sales |publisher=Detroit Free Press |date= |accessdate=2013-08-19 |archive-date=2013-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929092216/http://www.freep.com/article/20130625/BUSINESS/306250105/Top-7-pizza-chains-Little-Caesars-moves-up-a-notch |dead-url=no }}</ref>

截至2020年12月27日，「棒！约翰」在美国48个州和地区经营着5,400家Papa John's餐厅，其中包括588家公司拥有的餐厅（直营店）和4,812家特许经营餐厅（加盟店）。<ref name="美股之家">{{cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/pzza.html |title=全美第三大披萨连锁公司：棒约翰Papa John’s International(PZZA) |author= |publisher=美股之家 |date= |accessdate=2021-04-07 |dead-url=no |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116232837/http://www.mg21.com/pzza.html }}</ref>
